prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, minimalist flat 2D illustration. The scene is a humorous and whimsical beach day. A cartoon version of Jordan, based on the reference photo, is depicted mid-air, joyfully leaping over a small sandcastle with a stick in his mouth. He is wearing a plain brown hoodie and dark joggers. Below him, a cartoon version of Lao Lao, also based on the photo, is sitting on a beach blanket, laughing as she looks up at him. She wears a plain light blue sweatshirt and black pants. The beach is represented by simple, elegant shapes: a sweeping curve of pale sand against a flat, serene turquoise ocean. A few minimalist seagulls are drawn as simple 'm' shapes in the sky. Centered in the open space above the scene is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is clean, playful, and set against a soft, solid cream background.
